title: OCE Looking for Casual Players
body:
Hey guys.
Im looking for some casual people to play league with..I dont care what rank you are, although i wouldnt mind playing with some higher ranked people to try and pick up a few things, as im not the worlds strongest player.
Feel free to add me :)

Send me an add. Should be able to have some fun games
